262
00:15:29.947 --> 00:15:32.547
"t, e, i, u".

263
00:15:32.547 --> 00:15:35.447
Dengan huruf-huruf "teiu", maka itu pasti "teiuka"

264
00:15:35.447 --> 00:15:38.447
