323
00:18:37.547 --> 00:18:38.947
Apa maksudmu, "seharusnya"?

324
00:18:38.947 --> 00:18:41.047
Kau belum memeriksanya?

325
00:18:41.047 --> 00:18:45.747
Tidak. Kupikir aku meninggalkan ponselku di hotel,

326
00:18:45.747 --> 00:18:48.947
