336
00:19:13.447 --> 00:19:14.947
Kau sudah menghapusnya, bukan?

337
00:19:14.947 --> 00:19:17.947
Ya, tentu saja.

338
00:19:17.947 --> 00:19:19.347
Kau lihat!

339
00:19:19.347 --> 00:19:21.047
Benarkah?

340
00:19:21.047 --> 00:19:22.447
Bagaimanapun,

341
00:19:22.447 --> 00:19:24.647
